Package org.sfu.MotaGame.Bean

Class ImageData

java.lang.Object
org.sfu.MotaGame.Bean.ImageData
public class ImageData
extends Object
Image Data This class contains the integer representations of all of our sprites for the game, gets them and places them on the map, as well as dealing with the floor and direction.
